Mangalore Refinery Offers 81,000 Tons of September Oil Products

-- B y   Y e e   K a i   P i n
-- 
2011-07-26T00:55:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-26/mangalore-refinery-offers-81-000-tons-of-september-oil-products.html
India ’s  Mangalore Refinery &
Petrochemicals Ltd. (MRPL)  offered to sell 81,000 metric tons of oil
products for loading in September, the company said in documents
e-mailed to potential buyers.  Oil & Natural Gas Corp., the country’s largest crude
producer, owns 72 percent of Mangalore Refinery.  Details of the offers are as follow:  To contact the reporter on this story:
